{
  "stem": "9725.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I w-- I was with some of my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I, I really was not totally aware of exactly what happened at that moment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a great deal of, of confusion and chaos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our mothers were put into another enclosure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was near the railroad station where the circus used to come with a very large metal type stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And trucks appeared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And something rather curious and, for me, something that I could never really resolve in my happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a man by the name of Merin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Merin was someone who worked for the authorities, not a person to be much admired.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the story had it that he had a little daughter whom he adored.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans said that if he cooperates with them, he and the child are going to be saved.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, that was not the case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in any event, he cooperated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Merin was-- as a matter of fact, a little earlier my mother said to me, people say this is Merin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Go and ask him what, what is happening?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where we going?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember I went up and asked him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I asked him, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He sort of laughed and didn't give me an answer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I knew who he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wearing a black raincoat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can still see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a very, very slight, small man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the trucks appeared, and my friends-- all young girls-- and we were loaded on those trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard my mother's voice from that enclosure, and, and she was calling something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at this point, I realized that I was being taken away from my mother, so I jumped off the truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
